- **Odd & Positive**: It’s an odd, positive integer (ends in 3).


### 2. **Chronological Context**
- **Year**: 2113 is a future year (as of 2024). It will be a **common year** (not a leap year) starting on a **Monday** (if the Gregorian calendar remains in use).
